snippet.title: STEALTH THE GAME DEVLOG [SAGE 2024]
snippet.description:
This video was long in the making, those clips go as far back as 2023!

Music Used:

Bee Movie Game Soundtrack - First Flight
Let's Meet in the Mysterious Forest - Mario & Luigi Bowser's Inside Story
Sonic the Hedgehog 2: Hedgehog Heaven: 16. Super Sonic Ska (Super Sonic)
Kingdom Hearts 1.5 HD ReMix -Squirming Evil- 
Cool Edge (Night) - Sonic Unleashed

As long as you put your mind to it and with a bit of motivation, you can do almost anything.

#godot #sonicthehedgehog #indiegame #fangame #stealththehedgehog
